data.description: Like New home Boasting meticulously designed landscaping and a luxurious interior, this 5 bedroom, 3 1/2 bathroom home is truly a marvel to behold. Spanning over 2700 sq ft. of living space, this move-in ready residence effortlessly blends luxury and convenience. The modern elegance of the luxury vinyl plank flooring sets the tone as soon as you enter the home. The spacious great room and dining area create an inviting atmosphere, while the highlight of the home, the chef's kitchen, is impeccably designed with stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and rich cabinetry.The first-floor Master Suite offers a tranquil retreat, while the upstairs loft area provides a perfect space for relaxation or entertainment.Each bedroom is spacious and comfortable, and the bathrooms are beautifully appointed with large vanities. Outside, the private backyard offers a serene pond view and is enclosed by Charleston Style fencing, perfect for family activities or quiet evenings.  Located near various eateries such as McDonald's, Buffalo Wild Wings, Starbucks and Chic-Fil-A. Roper Hospital, and a Publix Super Market, this home offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Additionally, within the Pine Hills Subdivision, residents have access to resort-style amenities including pools, a clubhouse, playground and more. This stunning property is not to be missed so book your appointment before it's gone.  Builders warranty is still in place. Motivated Seller!!!!
